Package service

Class StaffService

java.lang.Object
service.StaffService
public class StaffService extends Object
The StaffService class provides functionality to manage staff data such as doctors, pharmacists, administrators, and nurses. It allows operations like retrieving staff details, adding new staff, removing staff, and updating staff attributes like name, password, and age.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Celeste Ho
